  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in the hot pot vessel over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the halved grape tomatoes, chopped parsley, and chopped cilantro.",
    "Pour in the lemon juice and add the salt, black pepper, and cumin.",
    "Stir well to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Serve the tagine hot, garnished with additional parsley and cilantro if desired."
